trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> class.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />.
The zero-based index where the <paramref name="port" /> parameter has been added.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="port" /> 매개 변수가 추가된 위치의 인덱스(0부터 시작)입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> for which to check collection membership.
Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" />이 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />의 멤버인지 여부를 나타내는 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" />가 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />의 멤버이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> serving as the destination for the copy action.
The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: 복사된 컬렉션을 배치하기 시작할 인덱스(0부터 시작)입니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" /> to a one-dimensional array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" />, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스(0부터 시작)에서 시작하여 전체 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />을 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> 형식의 1차원 배열에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> for which to search in the collection.
Searches for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" />을 검색하여 처음 나오는 항목의 인덱스(0부터 시작)를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer.
The zero-based index at which to insert the <c>port</c> parameter.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> instance to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> 인스턴스를 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />의 지정된 인덱스 위치에 추가합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 이미 있는 항목의 수가 컬렉션의 용량을 자동으로 새 요소를 삽입 하기 전에 내부 배열을 다시 할당 하 여 용량 배가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the specified <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 경우의 값은 `index` 매개 변수와 같으면 <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, 지정 된 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> 의 끝에 추가 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 삽입 지점 뒤에 있는 요소는 새 요소를 아래로 이동 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
\- or -
The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is greater than <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> instance specified by the parameter passed in.
trans-unit.target: 전달된 매개 변수에서 지정한 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> 인스턴스를 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> whose value is modified or returned.
Gets or sets the value of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 인덱스(0부터 시작)에서 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" />의 값을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The value of a port at the specified index.
The name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> returned.
Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> specified by its name.
A port specified by its name.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Port" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection" />.
This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 선형 검색; 수행 따라서 평균 실행 시간에 비례 하는 <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 제거 된 다음에 오는 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> 위로 이동 하 여 빈된 자리를 채웁니다.
